<A>__{we move through sharon's nearly dark apartment, its stillness in strange contrast to the manic trumpet riffs. we pan to find her curled in a chair, staring deeply, sadly, drinking a drink. as we pan, we discover she is looking at that mural of the mountains and through this to her thoughts, and then she makes a decision and rises and goes to the phone, punches in a number.}
